title: Thayer: Give Trump a chance
maintext:
Marge Vieselmeyer, 61, Chester, gas station operator
LAST YEAR: Vieselmeyer wanted “to make America great again.”
TODAY: Vieselmeyer says “Trump comes across wrong. What he says doesn’t sound right, but what he means is right. I’m still for him. I pray that they’ll give him a chance.”
